55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><strong>Option 1: Explain why me=
trics don=E2=80=99t exist</strong></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color:=
 rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">=E2=9C=85 =E2=80=9CThis =
was a client project and I didn=E2=80=99t have access to their analytics af=
ter handoff.=E2=80=9D =E2=9C=85 =E2=80=9CThe company didn=E2=80=99t have me=
asurement infrastructure in place for this feature.=E2=80=9D =E2=9C=85 =E2=
=80=9CThis was exploratory work that informed strategy but didn=E2=80=99t r=
esult in a shipped product.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;colo=
r: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">These are all legitima=
te. Just state them matter-of-factly.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;col=
or: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><strong>Option 2: Use=
 proxy metrics or observations</strong></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;c=
olor: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">If you don=E2=80=99=
t have hard numbers, look for other signals:</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">=E2=9C=85 =E2=
=80=9CThe redesigned form reduced the average support call length from 8 mi=
nutes to 3 minutes based on call center reports.=E2=80=9D =E2=9C=85 =E2=80=
=9CUser testing showed task completion time dropped from an average of 4 mi=
nutes to 90 seconds.=E2=80=9D =E2=9C=85 =E2=80=9CIn our usability tests, 4 =
out of 5 users completed the task successfully compared to 1 out of 5 with =
the old design.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55=
,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">These aren=E2=80=99t conversion ra=
tes or revenue numbers, but they=E2=80=99re real measurements.</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16=
px;"><strong>Option 3: Focus on the problem-solving process</strong></p><p =
style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-siz=
e: 16px;">If you have no outcome data at all, double down on showing your t=
hinking:</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height=
: 26px;font-size: 16px;">=E2=9C=85 =E2=80=9CI can=E2=80=99t measure the imp=
act because the project was paused before launch, but I can walk you throug=
h how I identified the core user problem and my rationale for the design de=
cisions.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);li=
ne-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">Your thinking process is actually what hi=
ring managers care about most. The metrics are just evidence that the think=
ing worked. If you have strong thinking, that=E2=80=99s 80% of what matters=
.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;=
font-size: 16px;"><strong>Option 4: Be upfront that it=E2=80=99s a learning=
 project</strong></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);li=
ne-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">If it=E2=80=99s bootcamp work or practice=
:</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;=
font-size: 16px;">=E2=9C=85 =E2=80=9CThis is a practice project I completed=
 during my UX bootcamp. It=E2=80=99s based on research I conducted with rea=
l users, but it=E2=80=99s not a shipped product.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">T=
hen show rigorous process. Show real research. Show thoughtful decisions. T=
he fact that it didn=E2=80=99t ship is fine if the work is solid.</p><block=
quote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #538cfa;margin: 20px 0;padding: 0;"><=
